Package org.factcenter.qilin.protocols.concrete

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DefaultOTExtender
    A convenience class that constructs a (passively-secure) OT extender server/client pair with sensible defaults (use ECNaorPinkas as seeds, RC4 for PRG, default Qilin digest for random oracle, etc.).
    ECNaorPinkasOT
    Elliptic-curve implementation of Naor-Pinkas OT.
    ECPedersenCoinflip
    Elliptic-curve implementation of the TrapdoorBlumTwoPartyGroupElementFlip using a PedersenCommitment as the trapdoor commitment scheme.
    ECPedersenCommitmentPoK
    Elliptic-curve implementation of TrapdoorHomomorphicCommitmentPoK using a PedersenCommitment as the trapdoor commitment scheme.
    ZpNaorPinkasOT
    A modular-arithmetic implementation of Naor-Pinkas OT.
